3.2 ARMD Trial: Visual Acuity

data(armd.wide, armd0, package = "nlmeU")
library(lattice)
armd0.subset <- subset(armd0, as.numeric(subject) %in% seq(1, 240, 10))
armd0.subset
xy1 <- xyplot(visual ~ jitter(time) | treat.f,
  groups = subject,
  data = armd0.subset,
  type = "l",
  lty = 1
)
update(xy1,
  xlab = "Time (in weeks)",
  ylab = "Visual acuity",
  grid = "h"
)
